snippet.title: Love 365: Find Your Story - Love Brings You Home PV
snippet.description:
Love Brings You Home

It's not like life's a complete disaster, but it's not all that fulfilling either. 
It was a day like any other, when he suddenly comes into your life and the love you've longed for is now on your doorstep. And before you know it, happiness and joy fills your everyday life.
A super attractive guy suddenly and unexpectedly shows up in your life.
"Since you took me in, I’ll comfort you from now on…"
Despite thinking this, his tender embrace is the start of your unusual new life together.
